{"word":"G5383 - φιλοπρωτεύω - philoprōteúō - fil-op-rote-yoo'-o - Love to have the preeminence","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φιλοπρωτεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">philoprōteúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">fil-op-rote-yoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Love to have the preeminence</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - முதன்மையாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to aspire after pre - eminence, to desire to be first"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G5384 - φίλος - phílos - fee'-los/5384\">G5384</a> and <a href=\"#/G4413 - πρῶτος - prōtos - pro'-tos/4413\">G4413</a>; to <i>be fond of being first</i>, that is, <i>ambitious</i> of distinction: - love to have the preeminence.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2705/2705\">G2705</a>, <a href=\"#/G5367/5367\">G5367</a>, <a href=\"#/G5368/5368\">G5368</a>, <a href=\"#/G5369/5369\">G5369</a>, <a href=\"#/G5370/5370\">G5370</a>, <a href=\"#/G5373/5373\">G5373</a>, <a href=\"#/G5377/5377\">G5377</a>, <a href=\"#/G5383/5383\">G5383</a>, <a href=\"#/G5384/5384\">G5384</a>, <a href=\"#/G5387/5387\">G5387</a>"}]}